Package com.mashery.trafficmanager.model.core

Provides classes and interfaces that comprise a view of the Mashery domain model from the Traffic Manager's point of view as it handles an API request.

See: Description

    API Endpoint being requested.

    Group of custom name/value pairs attached to domain model objects that support this capability.
